		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="414" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">猊兽凌空翻卷，朝玩家发射2刀水镜波刃，均造成<span color="#7fbfff">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">猊兽蜷尾，扫吹出数个锦标，与风蚀沙虫类似，其环围有余，每个均造成<span color="#7fffd7">60%,30%,12%,6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="991" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">猊兽前足一蹬，扬起暴风，造成<span color="#7fffd7">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="439" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">猊兽使唤风之仙力，召唤3个逆时针旋转的<span textDecoration="underline">灵风珠</span><span>，猊兽在原地持续鼓风，造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">60%</span><span>伤害；10s后，猊兽施放碎玉翠尘，造成大范围的</span><span color="#7fffd7">200%</span><span>伤害。<br/>尚存的灵风珠将转为移动的风涡，持续控制玩家的同时持续造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">30%</span><span>伤害。<br/>生命值</span><span color="#ffccbf">低于40%</span><span>时，会施放一次。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/隐山猊兽.assets/Image_14.png')" x="1391" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#15a7ae" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#15a7ae">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">猊兽击尾，在玩家处生成一个泉喷，造成<span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="441" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">猊兽进行<span textDecoration="underline">宁神嚣灭</span><span>，汲取水之仙力，在原地产生的泉眼处，泉眼持续造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">70%</span><span>伤害；泉眼还将在周围不断产生泉涌，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">70%</span><span>伤害；10s后，猊兽降下涂炭怒涛，生成7波潮涌，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">200%</span><span>伤害。<br/>生命值</span><span color="#ffcebf">低于70%</span><span>时，会施放一次。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="991" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">猊兽进行一次<span textDecoration="underline">宁神嚣灭</span><span>，朝玩家处游走一段距离，该技能也可作为技能「鸿泷山涧」的前摇。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">猊兽引风凌空，造成<span color="#7fffd7">80%</span><span>伤害，后以迅雷之势下落，一发激起千层浪，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
