		<RichText x="66" y="1164" width="442" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">宁神嚣灭：附着常驻的<span color="#7fbfff">水元素</span><span>与</span><span color="#7fffd7">4风元素</span><span>，此时允许被冻结。被冻结后，若采用碎冰等手段解除冻结状态，则会瘫痪9s。<br/>灵风珠：与风蚀沙虫一样，该珠可使用</span><span color="#ff9999">火</span><span>/</span><span color="#7fbfff">水</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffacff">雷</span><span>/</span><span color="#99ffff">冰</span><span>破除，全部破除后会瘫痪9s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/隐山猊兽.assets/Image_20.png')" x="64" y="160" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="5" y="1094" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="54" height="57" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">起身<br/>/爆发</p>
			</content>
